Example genome wide association study results at the FTO locus

Source: R/fto_locus_df.R
fto_locus_df.Rd

A dataset containing genome wide association study stummary results at the FTO locus on chromosome 16

Usage

fto_locus_df

Format

A data frame with 19119 rows and 9 variables:

chromosome

chromosome

position

position on chromosome

rsid

rsid number from dbSNP

effect_allele

effect allele (or reference allele)

other_allele

non-effect allele (or alternate allele)

eaf

effect allele frequenct (or minor allele frequency)

effect

effect of allele on outcome

std_err

standard error of the effect estimate

p_value

p-value of effect estimate
